As Mojo was relaxing, Tortoise threw a net over him! Then he went out to fetch firewood. Mojo could not move. "Help me, help me!" he cried.
Cock was near Tortoise's house. He heard Mojo shouting. He called "Mojo? Mojo?""Cock! Come and rescue me! responded Mojo. Cock hurried to where Mojo was trapped.
